---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 243
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Judgement=On Judging Others
By: Muhammad
---
Abu Jariya, an inhabitant of Basra, coming to Medina and being
convinced of the inspired mission of Muhammad asked him, according to
a Muslim historian, for some great rule of conduct.

\‘Speak evil of no one,’ answered the Prophet.
